  "instructions": [
    "Toast the rye bread slices in a dry skillet over medium heat until golden brown, about 2 minutes per side.",
    "In a bowl, mash the avocado with a fork until silky, then stir in minced garlic, lemon juice, sea salt, black pepper, and red pepper flakes.",
    "Drizzle olive oil over the mashed avocado mixture and fold in chopped cilantro.",
    "Spread the avocado mixture evenly onto the toasted rye slices.",
    "Sprinkle pumpkin seeds over the avocado spread.",
    "Place the remaining bread slice on top to form a sandwich.",
    "Cut the sandwich into halves along the diagonal edge.",
    "Serve immediately, optionally accompanied by a side of fresh fruit salad."
